# Data Dictionary

This document describes the key variables used in the Loan Default Analysis project.

| Column | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| Loan_Id | Unique identifier for each loan |
| Client_ID | Unique borrower identifier |
| loan_amnt | Amount approved for the loan |
| annual_inc | Borrower's annual income |
| loan_status | Indicates whether the loan was fully paid or defaulted |
| loan_grade | Credit grade assigned to the borrower |
| interest_rate | Annual interest rate charged |
| emp_length | Borrower's employment duration |
| home_ownership | Home ownership status |
| debt_income_ratio | Ratio of debt to annual income |
| outstanding_principal_balance | Remaining unpaid loan balance |
| purpose | Purpose of the loan |
